name: Saturn in Aquarius I
description:

• Gemini rising
• Saturn in Aquarius on the midheaven
• waning moon in Libra applying a trine to Saturn
• Gemini rising, and its ruler, Mercury, unafflicted in Aquarius

• cannabis
• six white stones
• the song "Saturn" by Sufjan Stevens, Nico Muhly, Bryce Dessner & James McAlister
